# Custom Theme
A minimal slideshow driven by a user-supplied `reveal.js` theme.

:::class "theme-marker"
Marker styled by the custom theme.
:::

:::class "extra-marker"
Marker styled by an extraCss file.
:::

:::class "asset-marker"
Marker with a background image from a bundled theme asset.
:::
